data.description:
Welcome to this charming ranch-style home situated in a tranquil neighborhood within the North Canton City school district. This home offers single-level living complemented by a full basement, ideal for storage or potential expansion. The recently renovated kitchen gives the home an open-concept feel and provides ample space for cooking and entertaining. Additionally, a dedicated workshop and a generously sized patio add functionality to this home, offering space for both work and relaxation, perfect for gatherings. This property combines peaceful surroundings with a flexible living space, catering to a variety of needs and lifestyles.

Additional details: Furnace replaced 2 years ago and Hot water tank 7 years ago. Roof was recently evaluated and in good shape.  Part of patio roof was replaced.
Home has new gutters, garage door, and fridge. Washer/dryer, home gym and a Simplicity 38 inch cut tractor are also included with the house.
